                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "​The launcher invites multiplayer action or can be used solo to experiment with unconventional stunts.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "​Kids will love learning to master the massive loop and the spring-loaded ramp. The landing adjusts along the track for a movable target and enhanced difficulty.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "​Includes one 1:64 scale Hot Wheels® car that fits in the launcher two ways -- the traditional back-in as well as horizontally.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "​Exciting challenges await kids 4 to 6 years old!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
